OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FBritons should prepare for a cyber-
OL,7,Fattack, severe weather event or a
OL,8,Fsimilar national crisis, which might
OL,9,Fleave resources such as food, power,
OL,10,For mobile phone signal scarce, the
OL,11,Fgovernment is to tell people.
OL,13,FAs the climate crisis triggers record-
OL,14,Fbreaking heatwaves in the UK, and as
OL,15,FAI evolves to allow more sophisticated
OL,16,Fways for criminals to carry out cyber-
OL,17,Fattacks, the government has said that
OL,18,Fthe UK is "being tested like never
OL,19,Fbefore".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
