OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FIn response to these growing threats,
OL,7,Fthe government will launch a national
OL,8,Fcampaign to educate Brits on how to
OL,9,Fprepare for an emergency.
OL,11,FDarren Jones, the chief secretary to
OL,12,Fthe prime minister, said it was
OL,13,Fimportant for Britons to be prepared
OL,14,Fto "help people keep themselves and
OL,15,Ftheir family safe" and allow emergency
OL,16,Fservices to "focus on helping the most
OL,17,Fvulnerable in communities" during
OL,18,Ftimes of crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FSeparately, the National Risk Register
OL,7,Fhas this week been updated with seven
OL,8,Fnew crises, bringing the total to 95.
OL,10,FWhat are the threats we face, and what
OL,11,Fis the government's advice to prepare
OL,12,Ffor an emergency?
OL,14,FWhat is the National Risk Register?
OL,16,FThe National Risk Register is the
OL,17,Fpublicly available version of the
OL,18,Fgovernment's National Security Risk
OL,19,FAssessment, setting out the key risks
OL,20,Ffacing the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FThe government stressed that it is
OL,7,F"not intended to be a prediction of
OL,8,Ffuture events," but it does provide an
OL,9,Findication of the most significant
OL,10,Fthreats to the country.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FWhat are the significant threats to
OL,18,Fthe UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
