PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FThe report notes that the UK faces "a
OL,7,Flandscape of volatile, diverse, and
OL,8,Finterconnected risks, ranging from
OL,9,Fgeopolitical instability to rapid
OL,10,Ftechnological change."
OL,12,F"In 2026 alone, the terrorism threat
OL,13,Fhas increased to severe, there has
OL,14,Falso been significant disruption to
OL,15,Foil and gas supplies from the Middle
OL,16,FEast and severe weather," it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FAs a result, the seven new threats
OL,7,Finclude the risks associated with
OL,8,Fcyber-attacks on data infrastructure,
OL,9,Fwater infrastructure and police
OL,10,Fsystems, as AI becomes more advanced.
OL,12,FAnother new threat is called "digital
OL,13,Fresilience failure", which the
OL,14,Fgovernment has said "builds on lessons
OL,15,Flearnt from the CrowdStrike IT outage
OL,16,Fin July 2024."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
