PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FThe outage, caused by a rogue software
OL,7,Fupdate by the US cybersecurity
OL,8,Fcompany, could be considered the
OL,9,Flargest in history. It caused millions
OL,10,Fof Windows systems to fail globally,
OL,11,Fresulting in planes being grounded,
OL,12,FGPs being unable to treat patients,
OL,13,Fand crashed payment systems.
OL,15,FThe threat of disruption to Russian
OL,16,Fgas supplies is one factor that has
OL,17,Fbeen removed from the register,
OL,18,F"reflecting that the UK has reduced
OL,19,Fits reliance on Russian gas."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
