PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FWeather remains a credible hazard,
OL,7,Fwith the UK seeing record-breaking
OL,8,Ftemperatures this year and wildfires
OL,9,Fin the last week.
OL,11,FJones said: "This year we saw
OL,12,Ftemperatures across the UK breaking
OL,13,Frecords in May, only to be exceeded
OL,14,Fagain in June", telling Parliament
OL,15,Fthat the speed of climate change
OL,16,Fshould not be underestimated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
