PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FRobert Palmer, deputy director of
OL,7,Fcampaign group Uplift, this week said:
OL,8,F"Excessive heatwaves will get more
OL,9,Ffrequent and intense the longer we
OL,10,Fstay hooked on fossil fuels."
OL,12,FWhat does it look like to "be
OL,13,Fprepared"?
OL,15,FThe government is urging the public to
OL,16,Ftake "small but important steps", and
OL,17,FITV understands it is designed to
OL,18,Fbuild upon previously issued guidance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
