PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FThe current advice can be read here,
OL,7,Fand suggests several steps that can be
OL,8,Ftaken to prepare for potential
OL,9,Femergencies. The government guidance
OL,10,Fat the moment includes:
OL,12,FThey also suggest putting together an
OL,13,F"emergency kit of items at home",
OL,14,Fincluding a battery or wind-up torch,
OL,15,Fportable charger, first aid kit, non-
OL,16,Fperishable food and a battery-powered
OL,17,For wind-up radio.
OL,19,FCall 999 if you or someone else is in
OL,20,Fimmediate danger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
