PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FWhen will the new advice be given?
OL,8,FIt is not clear when the new campaign
OL,9,Fwill launch, but the move has been
OL,10,Fpraised by the National Emergencies
OL,11,FTrust, which is expected to work
OL,12,Falongside the government on the
OL,13,Fproject.
OL,15,F"This is a significant opportunity to
OL,16,Fstrengthen preparedness across the
OL,17,Fcountry, helping people and
OL,18,Fcommunities build the knowledge,
OL,19,Fconfidence and resilience they need to
OL,20,Fprepare for emergencies before they
OL,21,Fhappen," they said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
