PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784162882
OL,3,CWhy Britons are being told to prepare
OL,4,Cfor cyber-attacks and extreme weather
OL,6,FMinisters were warned by the National
OL,7,FPreparedness Commission (NPC) in May
OL,8,Fthat Britain's supply chains were
OL,9,Funprepared for crises associated with
OL,10,Fthe war in Russia, severe consequences
OL,11,Fof climate change and the possibility
OL,12,Fof another pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
